      "name": "FDA generic centrifugal pump flow field validation against PIV measurements",
      "description": "Velocity field predictions compared against particle image velocimetry data at 3 operating points. Mean absolute error 8.2% across all measurement planes.",
      "outcome": "conditional-pass"
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/vad-pump-hemolysis-validation",
