      "name": "Hemolysis index validation against in-vitro loop experiments",
      "description": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis compared to five in-vitro loop experiments. Systematic underprediction observed at high shear regimes; Monte Carlo bands do not fully enclose experimental scatter.",
      "outcome": "fail"
    }
  ],
  "hasCredibilityFactor": [
