      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence and hemolysis sub-model selection justified with literature evidence specific to VAD flow regimes; alternative model forms evaluated.",
      "rationale": "Flagged as epistemic gap. k-omega SST turbulence model selected without comparison to scale-resolving alternatives. Hemolysis power-law model not compared to strain-based or energy dissipation alternatives at MRL 5."
    },
