    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors assessed; all seven exhibit achieved levels below required levels. Six factors flagged as epistemic gaps and marked not-assessed. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification partially executed but convergence not confirmed. The aggregate credibility profile does not meet the threshold for regulatory submission at MRL 5. Assessment formally recorded as Not accepted pending remediation of identified gaps.",
